          <p>FTB Tennessee is dedicated to developing elite baseball players through discipline, hard work, and competitive excellence. We focus on building character, fostering teamwork, and preparing athletes for long-term success.</p>
          <p>As part of the prestigious FTB organization, we provide unparalleled exposure to college scouts and professional teams, helping players achieve their dreams of playing at the next level.</p>
          <p>Our experienced coaching staff, comprised of former collegiate and professional players, brings expertise and mentorship to every aspect of training and game strategy.</p>
