          <div class="owner-content">
            <h3>Will Haynie</h3>
            <p>Will Haynie played at the University of Alabama, leading the team with 10 home runs in 2015 and 2016. He earned All-Cape Cod Team honors in the Cape Cod League and was drafted by the Colorado Rockies in 2016. After playing professionally until 2019, Will now coaches athletes at collegiate, professional, and elite high school levels, focusing on hitting, fielding, and sportsmanship.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="owner-card">
          <img src="https://placehold.co/350x250?text=Justin+Wilson" alt="Justin Wilson" loading="lazy">
          <div class="owner-content">
            <h3>Justin Wilson</h3>
            <p>Justin Wilson, from Murfreesboro, TN, played at Volunteer State Community College and Vanderbilt University before pitching in the Yankees organization from 2018 to 2023, finishing in Double-A with a 3.45 ERA. He now brings his pitching expertise to player development at FTB Tennessee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
